    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-12-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-12-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="1290"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1290">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.115/32.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consular
                        Agent <persName type="to">Taylor</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 13, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Treaty of 1831 no longer in force. Report to Department if there is any apparent
                    illegal procedure or discrimination against foreigners in connection with levy
                    of taxes by local authorities; also if nationals of any country are exempted
                    from payment of taxes by virtue of treaty provisions or otherwise.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
